## Guidelines

- **Specs before code:** Do not implement without corresponding spec entries
- **Run roles in order:** architect → ui-designer → interface-designer → security-analyst → edge-case-analyst → senior-developer
- **Atomic changes:** Keep changes small and focused
- **Update tasks.md:** Mark tasks in_progress when starting, complete when done
- **Commit message format:** Use conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, etc.)
